-- Microsoft's Baym Discusses Social Media Fundraising (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-10-16T20:35:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-16/microsoft-s-baym-discusses-social-media-fundraising-audio-.html
Nancy Baym, a principal researcher 
with the social media collective at Microsoft Research New 
England, discusses how musicians have used social media to 
promote their music and raise money. Baym speaks to Bloomberg's 
 Kathleen Hays  and Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays 
Advantage."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 05:09
 